e, un dîner en famille, ou un moment partagé entre amis, nous vous promettons une expérience authentique — celle qui donne envie de revenir.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:18px\"><strong>📍 22 Rue Hafid Essalafi, Casablanca 20370, Morocco</strong></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"gallery\" class=\"gallery\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#f5d7a0\">Galerie</div>\n      <h2>L'œil dans l'assiette</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#aaa\">Quelques instants capturés chez nous.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gal-grid\"><div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGwZ__9bjUauEzFwv2jU5oVnIyJYVUtp958hl09qvmBBsRi8O1bcDoDfH4FPj5oI6k775kYzIP_KkonqX1tthX2HnTcIXz5JK1bOscv0_ddGdbzGvCxEq81ERzA3VVsBmxIl5iS=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Thami Burger\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipOCaYFQbR_upJxNh-2N1l6WDFdordqWfAgD-V0n=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Thami Burger\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGJ8EAZNwcZRkZ_OT6W1oOZmy6WmHBfX2fnrqa4z_8KZl6mGYp7Ow1k8QKvBW2cLogE3yVDHr11gN3QUxTyF_T7nouTNai3pwS1p7IZIooyHN-9AK2tnIglcoZMlRLYqEAFTJcFfpPaZRk=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Thami Burger\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAHhjNJZLELURxg9c4jSWc9xlmBr0j1lokM3M6ixYD_sUuXhBmFJ72qnxeWzmtWtobh3smS_gxsuj0OOQyxjCALNRdOtOt9Vn3TFB5q2O5UDRC2gEA5C80S2eeDlpGMj_m98GvqwYA=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Thami Burger\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/proxy/xRA-GSjd5dHTtqdzuIUP4Po4RJrxWUpWB8MWn2CxW9bCWTDtr1-xO8XDLnpFch7A8hYGGCVJvndsBVdZklq2hdXGvBLz_npyWQGlzLjODVhnQXWloVqp_-VxXriyKjGsFJUWIisINzDzjBGpuP3hLNDXEROQrpg=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Thami Burger\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><i